item.title: Welcome
item.description: Introduction Hi there! I’m Dhemas, an Indonesian software engineer. I grew up in a small town called Salatiga, Central Java, Indonesia. I really like to tinker with computer since I was a child. Playing games (SkiFree to Age of Empires II) in my dad’s office computer, then learn some office softwares, buying a floppy disk to save my diary (encrypted with Webdings font!), buying PC magazines, leads to learn how to assemble my own computer and do an OS install.
